{"tid":52094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有啲人會咁賤，連流浪貓狗唔放過？","createTime":"2016-12-23T18:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T00:36:52.000Z","uid":20625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98af31ab192ce73cfdde4a879c947b9508d54e83","tid":52094,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:15:26.000Z","msg":"有時見到新聞話有人殘害貓狗都已經好嬲，但係自己都做唔到咩野去幫啲貓狗<br />\n有時都會係啲污糟既地方見到流浪貓狗<br />\n唯有希望佢地被有心人帶走<br />\n但係有時係FB見到啲Page，專門去搵俾人遺棄既流浪貓狗<br />\n然後叫漁農處去捉，大多數既結果大家都估到：人道毀滅<br />\n<br />\n有時見到呢啲，就會覺得自己好無力<br />\n唔通真係要趕盡殺絕？乜貓同狗唔係人類最好既朋友或者玩伴咩？<br />\n成日見到巴絲打執到貓狗，我有時都想執到<br />\n但係諗深一層，自己仲係學生，未必抽到時間去照顧佢<br />\n經濟上未必支持到養貓（由其到時打針、絕育等等）<br />\n又諗到其實我執到就等於有人遺棄佢<br />\n果下真係好Sad好迷惘<br />\n<br />\n但願呢啲遺棄貓狗同埋對流浪貓狗都唔放過巴人渣<br />\n下世都要受番呢啲流浪貓狗既痛苦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/020157_a1efdf4b0199ad0fcb11f800976f8e4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F020157_a1efdf4b0199ad0fcb11f800976f8e4b.jpg&h=c2880320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個Facebook Page會特登出Post話自己已經聯絡漁農處又乜又柒<br />\n其實就係逼漁農處一定要跟程序做，唔可以「漏單」<br />\n每個Post都會有人留言鬧佢<br />\n比較出位既都會被Cap低<br />\n佢仲會聲稱已經報警同埋引用相關法律條文（恐嚇等）<br />\n希望大家幫幫手，打開你地既Facebook舉報佢<br />\n集合LIHKG既力量我相信可以令呢個Page被移除<br />\n<br />\n動物被馴養成寵物<br />\n為既係要取悅人類<br />\n佢地曾經取悅了人類<br />\n但係仍然避唔開被遺棄既命運<br />\n佢地被遺棄係人類所鑄成既錯<br />\n點解仲要俾人趕盡殺絕？"},{"pid":"d5e99a6c9f7971aa76a393b813be4dae1cd90fc8","tid":52094,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n好撚無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d929190636133fd8e898c012e33c544a939bede2","tid":52094,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"漏左超連結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AA%E7%8A%AC%E9%9A%BB-%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-Report-straydogs-1794284024118598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E7%258A%25AC%25E9%259A%25BB-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-Report-straydogs-1794284024118598%2F&d=OozWam4SwW%2B8H43GDGsGhwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=81dac596\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AA%E7%8A%AC%E9%9A%BB-%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-Report-straydogs-1794284024118598/</a>"},{"pid":"2d20c5bb8f813577e9f0cf33d2fa7a83b4f8b4e1","tid":52094,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:18:21.000Z","msg":"因為冇錢冇資源養， 放生又怕變流浪問題<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997ddcb71ea37f88b42db9ab7aff30645cc8752e","tid":52094,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:21:07.000Z","msg":"如果嗰條友真係受過流浪狗滋擾<br />\n咁佢舉報有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndirty work 就人地做，光環就你拎"},{"pid":"c424d71117ee81fa433b6c4c268bb9bf1ad801e7","tid":52094,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得係漁農處問題多d"},{"pid":"d24cca0b21f8df9f9876a6fa514abece4d931eb9","tid":52094,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母趕盡殺絕既正仆街，死左永世係地獄受苦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ba71b8b8122c4ac6472c32092168b162872d98","tid":52094,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:35:12.000Z","msg":"個page好似係劉冠傳(極醜惡大叔)開既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c92ec0c2127c3d76029f6760b441bfaef93a0a0","tid":52094,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:38:21.000Z","msg":"好賤呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb45c8a11e88307fe16f51ee78cd10aa4aa5d06","tid":52094,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:40:45.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街<br />\n<br />\n殺左又唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f1751e540b0b11c08ae5ac800a93df8db7aded","tid":52094,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:10:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9adca22e0fde3ff2879cbe6cd91df8085b3c6236","tid":52094,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:11:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e153aeb611f70c9a558f78c8af260282515c4687","tid":52094,"uid":15993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>流浪貓冇攻擊性，先唔討論住，不過流浪狗有攻擊性，咬到人邊個負責？樓主負責醫藥費？<br />\n<br />\n我知實有人話：都未咬到人，應該咬到人之後先人道毀滅肇事狗隻，但唔係應該未雨綢繆，防範於未然咩？我都試過幾次差d俾流浪狗咬，超驚險</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人都有可能出街斬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔洗未雨綢繆<br />\n<br />\n做到嘅事只係估算風險出現既機率同Event嘅嚴重性<br />\n<br />\n不過點去量度同點決定thresholds又係一個無答案既問題<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好簡單化事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申  殺唔殺我無所謂不過問題唔係咁簡單"},{"pid":"80dc7da1d2451560f26bd43d7fd9e32ef14376c1","tid":52094,"uid":42189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都認同樓主嘅<br />\n其實唔只貓狗，其他動物都係。<br />\n應該尊重生命。<br />\n不過耐何好多人都覺得人類永遠站在最高位，而且思想自私。睇到世界上咁多動物接近絕種就心痛。"}]}